title: UNC Chapel Hill Student Newspaper: ICE Is 'Biggest' Public Safety Threat During Chinese Virus Pandemic
description: The editorial board of the student newspaper for the UNC Chapel Hill claimed that U.S. Immigration and Customs Enforcement (ICE) is the "biggest" threat to public safety, even during the Chinese virus pandemic.
content:
The editorial board of the student newspaper for the UNC Chapel Hill claimed that U.S. Immigration and Customs Enforcement (ICE) is the “biggest” threat to public safety, even during the Chinese virus pandemic.
